import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Button, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, CardActions, Avatar } from '@mui/material';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import { HowToReg, Search, ContactSupport, School, Person, Group, Event, Assignment, Description, Receipt, PersonAdd } from '@mui/icons-material';

import CountUp from 'react-countup';

const images = [
  "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?w=1600",
  "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=1600",
  "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?w=1600",
  "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543466835-00a7907e9de3?w=1600",
  "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511367461989-f85a21fda167?w=1600"
];

const ImageSlider = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        position: "relative",
        color: "white",
        textAlign: "center",
        overflow: "hidden",
        margin: 0,
        padding: 0,
        height: "500px"
      }}
    >
      {/* Add your image slider implementation here */}
    </Box>
  );
};

function HomePage() {
  return (
    <Box>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box sx={{ position: 'relative' }}>
        <ImageSlider />

        <Box
          sx={{
            position: 'absolute',
            top: '50%',
            left: '50%',
            transform: 'translate(-50%, -50%)',
            width: '100%',
            zIndex: 1,
            textAlign: 'center'
          }}
        >
          <Container maxWidth="md">
            <Typography
              variant="h2"
              component="h1"
              sx={{
                fontWeight: 'bold',
                mb: 3,
                textShadow: '2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)',
                color: 'white',
              }}
            >
              Welcome to CampusLink
            </Typography>
            <Typography
              variant="h5"
              sx={{
                mb: 4,
                textShadow: '1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)',
                color: 'white',
              }}
            >
              Your Campus Management System
            </Typography>
          </Container>
        </Box>
      </Box>

      {/* Quick Actions Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 5 }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h3"
          component="h2"
          textAlign="center"
          gutterBottom
          sx={{ mb: 6 }}
        >
          Quick Actions
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent>
                <School sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Student Portal
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Access student resources and services
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={RouterLink} 
                  to="/login" 
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  Login
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Person sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Faculty Portal
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Access faculty resources and tools
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={RouterLink} 
                  to="/login" 
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  Login
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Group sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Department Portal
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Access departmental resources
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={RouterLink} 
                  to="/login" 
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  Login
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Event sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Events & Announcements
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  View upcoming campus events
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={RouterLink} 
                  to="/events" 
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  View Events
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>

      {/* Statistics Section */}
      <Box
        sx={{
          py: 8,
          bgcolor: '#f5f5f5',
          mt: 8
        }}
      >
        <Container>
          <Typography
            variant="h3"
            component="h2"
            textAlign="center"
            gutterBottom
            sx={{ mb: 6 }}
          >
            Campus Statistics
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={4} textAlign="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
              <Avatar sx={{ 
                width: 64, 
                height: 64, 
                bgcolor: '#1a237e',
                mb: 2
              }}>
                <Person sx={{ fontSize: 32 }} />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom>
                <CountUp start={0} end={5000} duration={2.5} />+
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6">
                Students
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
              <Avatar sx={{ 
                width: 64, 
                height: 64, 
                bgcolor: '#1a237e',
                mb: 2
              }}>
                <Assignment sx={{ fontSize: 32 }} />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom>
                <CountUp start={0} end={150} duration={2.5} />+
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6">
                Courses
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
              <Avatar sx={{ 
                width: 64, 
                height: 64, 
                bgcolor: '#1a237e',
                mb: 2
              }}>
                <Description sx={{ fontSize: 32 }} />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom>
                <CountUp start={0} end={100} duration={2.5} />+
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6">
                Research Projects
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
              <Avatar sx={{ 
                width: 64, 
                height: 64, 
                bgcolor: '#1a237e',
                mb: 2
              }}>
                <Receipt sx={{ fontSize: 32 }} />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom>
                <CountUp start={0} end={50} duration={2.5} />+
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6">
                Departments
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Services Section */}
      <Box
        sx={{
          py: 8,
          bgcolor: '#ffffff',
          mt: 8
        }}
      >
        <Container>
          <Typography
            variant="h3"
            component="h2"
            textAlign="center"
            gutterBottom
            sx={{ mb: 6 }}
          >
            Campus Services
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={4}>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                <CardContent>
                  <PersonAdd sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                    Admissions
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    Apply for admission to our programs
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions>
                  <Button 
                    component={RouterLink} 
                    to="/admissions" 
                    variant="outlined" 
                    color="primary"
                  >
                    Learn More
                  </Button>
                </CardActions>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                <CardContent>
                  <Receipt sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                    Academic Records
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    Access academic transcripts and records
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions>
                  <Button 
                    component={RouterLink} 
                    to="/records" 
                    variant="outlined" 
                    color="primary"
                  >
                    Access Records
                  </Button>
                </CardActions>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                <CardContent>
                  <Event sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#1a237e', mb: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                    Campus Events
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    Stay updated with campus activities
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions>
                  <Button 
                    component={RouterLink} 
                    to="/events" 
                    variant="outlined" 
                    color="primary"
                  >
                    View Events
                  </Button>
                </CardActions>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default HomePage;
